We used both a concatenation- and a coalescent-based phylogenomic method to construct a reliable phylogeny using the GBS data of 140 non-hybrid\n              Phytophthora\n              isolates. Hybrid species were subsequently connected to their progenitors in this phylogenetic tree. In this study we demonstrate the application of two validated techniques (GBS and flow cytometry) for relatively low cost but high resolution identification of hybrids and their phylogenetic relations.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Van Poucke, Kris", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Haegeman, Annelies", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Goedefroit, Thomas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Focquet, Fran", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Leus, Leen", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jung, Mar\u00edlia Horta", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nave, Corina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Redondo, Miguel Angel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Husson, Claude", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kostov, Kaloyan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lyubenova, Aneta", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Christova, Petya", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chandelier, Anne", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Slavov, Slavcho", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "de Cock, Arthur", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bonants, Peter", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Werres, Sabine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Palau, Jon\u00e0s Oliva", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mar\u00e7ais, Benoit", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jung, Thomas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stenlid, Jan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ruttink, Tom", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Heungens, Kurt", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 2", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d8a80f5c71a73a71567a88396a24f016", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/